Dorothy Shay https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Shay 0 Dorothy Shay (April 11, 1921 – October 22, 1978) was an American popular comedic recording artist in the late 1940s and early 1950s, who later became a character actress. She was known as the "Park Avenue Hillbilly".
